name: Maze (itch) (SiddhantStudios)
description: A maze game created by Siddhant Verma. This game has 15 levels with 3 enemies each different from previous. You can collect three type of collectibles diamond, coin and rings. 3 enemies Ghost, Spider and Skeleton. Some extra things like boulders, moving walls, holes, doors, bombs and trigger. Did you can solve the Maze of this game. If yes what are you waiting for! Collect as much collectibles. You can take screenshot of your highscore by pressing F9. Download this game
